title: Russo Radio in for #92Noon - Lapanta / Hankinson / McCain / Birk / Graff
description:
The Athletic's Michael Russo fills in for Paul Allen on this late June Wednesday.

The show is filled with great guests, plenty of hockey conversation, and a Birk-included Athletic Hour!
